Wood-Plastic Grille is a building material that has been well-received in recent years. It is healthy and environmentally friendly, has novel shapes has obvious decorative effects, and has been familiar and recognized by the market. Wood-plastic grilles are waterproof, flame-retardant, insect-proof, and anti-aging, so they can be decorated in almost any corner. Its unique line sense and decorative effect are very suitable for use as ceilings, wall panels, and floors. It can effectively increase the fullness of the space, and raise the floor height and overall grade. Of course, in addition to being used for home decoration, wood-plastic grilles are also widely used in larger decoration projects such as ecological gardens, museums, hotels, and conference rooms.
